@monster pos=18 name=ゾンビ
@monster pos=19 name=ゾンビ
@monster pos=20 name=ゾンビ
@callbattle escape=false bgm=crisis gameover=true

@wait time=500
@se f=roar
@fgf c=9010 left=450 top=80
@wait time=500
[texton]
[リーダー f=06]「They're still coming...!」[k]
We took out the enemies in front of us, but more undead keep coming![k]
[textoff]
